            "source": [
                "# 🏀 Ankece AI - Basketball Detection Training Pipeline (YOLOv8)\n",
                "Ce notebook permet d'entraîner un modèle YOLOv8 personnalisé pour détecter le ballon, le panier et le joueur, optimisé pour l'application Ankece.\n",
                "\n",
                "## 1. Setup Environment"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "!pip install ultralytics roboflow opencv-python"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "markdown",
            "metadata": {},
            "source": [
                "## 2. Dataset Roboflow (Ankece Custom)\n",
                "Connectez-vous à Roboflow pour récupérer votre dataset annoté."
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "from roboflow import Roboflow\n",
                "rf = Roboflow(api_key=\"VOTRE_ROBOFLOW_API_KEY\")\n", project = rf.workspace(\"michael-moussaoui\").project(\"ankece-basketball\")\n",
                "dataset = project.version(1).download(\"yolov8\")"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "markdown",
            "metadata": {},
            "source": [
                "## 3. Training YOLOv8 (Fine-Tuning)\n",
                "On utilise `yolov8n.pt` (Nano) comme base pour garantir une performance fluide en temps réel sur mobile."
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "from ultralytics import YOLO\n",
                "\n",
                "# Load model\n",
                "model = YOLO('yolov8n.pt')\n",
                "\n",
                "# Train with Ankece Dataset\n",
                "model.train(\n",
                "    data=f\"{dataset.location}/data.yaml\",\n",
                "    epochs=100,\n",
                "    imgsz=640,\n",
                "    batch=16,\n",
                "    name='ankece_basketball_v1'\n",
                ")"
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "markdown",
            "metadata": {},
            "source": [
                "## 4. Export for Mobile (Ankece Integration)\n",
                "Export vers ONNX (pour AI-Service) et TFLite (pour le futur client mobile direct)."
            ]
        },
        {
            "cell_type": "code",
            "execution_count": null,
            "metadata": {},
            "outputs": [],
            "source": [
                "# Export to ONNX / TFLite\n",
                "model.export(format='onnx', imgsz=640)\n",
                "model.export(format='tflite', imgsz=640)"
            ]
        },
